        <title type="html"><![CDATA[XTC任意版本root方法]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.xrzyun.top/post/xtc-root/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.xrzyun.top/post/xtc-root/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-10-03T12:30:30.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>刷机有风险，玩机需谨慎。如果变砖作者概不负责。</strong></p>
<h2 id="条件">条件</h2>
<p>聪明的脑子、灵活的双手、会用QFIL<a href="https://wearandme.com:8888/QFIL%E5%88%B7%E6%9C%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/QFIL%E5%88%B7%E6%9C%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7.7z">[下载]</a><a href="https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=utf-8&amp;f=8&amp;rsv_bp=1&amp;tn=baidu&amp;wd=QFIL%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B">[教程]</a>、刷过sboot<a href="https://coding-net-production-file-1257242599.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/2c8adea0-cf3b-11ea-abb4-3ba29736327b.zip?sign=q-sign-algorithm%3Dsha1%26q-ak%3DAKIDay83lFmaS6Y4LTdzMVO1SdZOyJSNOYpr%26q-sign-time%3D1595766416%3B1595770016%26q-key-time%3D1595766416%3B1595770016%26q-header-list%3D%26q-url-param-list%3Dresponse-content-disposition%3Bresponse-expires%26q-signature%3D80b6cd415e05cc18bd401cb365ccb7f0da15fb71&amp;response-content-disposition=attachment%3Bfilename%3DXTC-SBoot-RV1.5.zip&amp;response-expires=Wed%2C%2029%20Jul%202020%2000%3A26%3A56%20GMT">[下载]</a>。</p>
<h2 id="提取固件已有固件可忽略">提取固件（已有固件可忽略）</h2>
<p>1、（移除root，升级至最新固件）<br>
2、连接电脑，打开QFIL，9008模式提取system分区（和userdata分区）<a href="https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=utf-8&amp;f=8&amp;rsv_bp=1&amp;tn=baidu&amp;wd=QFIL%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA">[提取方法]</a></p>
<h2 id="正式开工">正式开工</h2>
<p>3、进9008，回到可刷sboot的版本，刷入sboot.img和recovery.img<a href="https://xrzyun.coding.net/api/share/download/4661641d-9490-4dac-aeda-f488e7f1ef44">[下载]</a>（和备份的       userdata.bin）[不会刷看<a href="https://www.baidu.com/s?ie=utf-8&amp;f=8&amp;rsv_bp=1&amp;tn=baidu&amp;wd=QFIL%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B">教程</a>]<br>
(4、回到系统，输入<code>adb reboot recovery</code>确认能进入rec)<br>
5、9008刷之前提取的system.bin<br>
6、开机查看：新系统和magisk都在</p>
<h2 id="其它">其它</h2>
<p><a href="/post/xtcuproot-Q&A/">可能出现的意外及解决方法</a><br>
tips：作者z5q测试成功，其他机型请自测。（图有空再补）</p>
<h2 id="鸣谢">鸣谢</h2>
<ul>
